exceptions.exn: In environment a : Term Unable to unify "SysPrf PA (equal Zero (Succ a))" with "SysPrf PA (notH (equal (Succ a) Zero))".

original: intros a. apply (eqSym PA (Succ a) Zero). apply nnE. unfold PA at 1. unfold PA1. apply cp2. apply (absurd1 PA (equal (Succ a) Zero)). apply nnI. apply (contradiction PA (equal (Succ a) Zero)). admit. apply noMiddle.
